[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    130[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    131[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Problem:** The recipe mentions "batch (process notes in bulk for research or quality measurement)" as a deployment pattern but only shows the real-time Lambda-orchestrated architecture. Research workloads processing 100K+ historical notes need different orchestration (Step Functions, SageMaker Batch Transform, parallel processing).
