[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    140[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    141[0m:[38;5;10m[49m VPC requirements are explicit: Lambda and SageMaker in VPC with VPC endpoints for S3, Comprehend Medical, DynamoDB, and CloudWatch Logs. This covers the critical data path. All API calls specified over TLS. The separation of training data (S3) from inference (endpoint) is clean.
