[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    165[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Fix:** Add brief note: "Deploy Lambda and SageMaker endpoint across at least 2 AZs for production resilience. SageMaker real-time endpoints with multiple instances automatically distribute across AZs."
