[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 1. **Lambda DLQ (A1):** Operational stability. Silent note loss is unacceptable for clinical systems.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    218[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 2. **Conflict resolution (A3):** Clinical correctness. Current logic can produce wrong "resolved" assertions.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 3. **Review queue guidance (A2):** Operational sustainability. Without it, the system generates an unmanageable workload.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 4. **PHI retention (S1):** Compliance requirement. Straightforward to add.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 5. **SageMaker VPC (N1):** PHI in transit concern for real-time inference.
