[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | 9 | MEDIUM | Networking | Prerequisites, VPC row | SageMaker Runtime VPC endpoint not listed. If endpoint is not VPC-configured, Lambda cannot invoke it without VPC endpoint or NAT gateway. | Clarify: VPC-configured endpoint (preferred) eliminates need for separate VPC endpoint. Otherwise add `sagemaker.runtime` interface endpoint. |
